From: Nickel Browser Team <team@nickel-browser.org>
Date: Thu, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Nickel Browser: VPN Integration (WireGuard/OpenVPN)

This patch adds VPN client UI for WireGuard and OpenVPN configurations.
Users can import their own VPN configs - no built-in VPN service.

